# GeoIP2 database update configuration
# Generated at container start from environment variables.
#
# Set these environment variables to enable automatic database updates:
#   GEOIP_ACCOUNT_ID    MaxMind account ID
#   GEOIP_LICENSE_KEY   MaxMind license key
#
# Without a license key, the container uses the legacy GeoLite database
# bundled in the geoip-database package (no updates, may be stale).
#
# Get a free account + license key at: https://www.maxmind.com/en/geolite2/signup
